      "raw": "# For d=8: tr(gamma^{kl}gamma^{mn}) where gamma^{kl} = (gamma^k gamma^l - gamma^l gamma^k)/2",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "For the spin connection curvature Omega_{ij} = (1/4) R_{ijkl} gamma^{kl}: tr(Omega_{ij}Omega^{ij}) = (1/16) R_{ijkl} R^{ij}_{mn} tr(gamma^{kl}gamma^{mn})",
