      "raw": "# Using tr(gamma^a gamma^b gamma^c gamma^d) = 2^{d/2}(delta_{ab}delta_{cd}",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "= (1/4)[tr(gamma^k gamma^l gamma^m gamma^n) - tr(gamma^k gamma^l gamma^n gamma^m) - tr(gamma^l gamma^k gamma^m gamma^n) + tr(gamma^l gamma^k gamma^n gamma^m)]",
