      "raw": "= 16(delta_{ab}delta_{cd} - delta_{ac}delta_{bd} + delta_{ad}delta_{bc})",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "Using tr(gamma^a gamma^b gamma^c gamma^d) = 2^{d/2}(delta_{ab}delta_{cd} - delta_{ac}delta_{bd} + delta_{ad}delta_{bc}) for d=8:",
