      "severity": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "eq_9770",
      "raw": "# Actually: tr(gamma^k gamma^l gamma^m gamma^n) = 16(d_{kl}d_{mn} - d_{km}d_{ln} + d_{kn}d_{lm})",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "- 16(delta_{kn}delta_{lm} - delta_{km}delta_{nl} + delta_{kl}delta_{mn})  [swap m,n on second] Wait, let me be more careful.",
